China Targets Polysilicon Companies for Elimination, 21st Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-23T23:58:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/china-targets-polysilicon-companies-for-elimination-21st-says.html
China plans to eliminate polysilicon
companies that do not satisfy production size,  energy efficiency 
and environmental criteria set by the Ministry of Industry and
Information Technology, the 21st Century Business Herald
reported, citing an unidentified person from  GCL-Poly Energy
Holdings Ltd. (3800)   Those that do not meet criteria must reform or be
eliminated within two years, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  